{"tid":1228664,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"職工盟話星期一繼續罷工！！！","createTime":"2019-06-15T17:39:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T03:02:39.000Z","uid":94327,"like":107,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"7e20ce54f02f6e788fce74a4f222c4ed10c8dd84","tid":1228664,"uid":94327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:39:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/169276086446006/posts/2959245247449062?s=1687043028&amp;sfns=mo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F169276086446006%2Fposts%2F2959245247449062%3Fs%3D1687043028%26sfns%3Dmo&d=YAxVOUHAW5%2FtYfR1oVoe2%2BSm5IdDYGcDmrHSDEWRKV4%3D&h=a9048ad9\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/169276086446006/posts/2959245247449062?s=1687043028&amp;sfns=mo</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BOTeGus.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBOTeGus.png&h=e87a9c3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n職工盟仍然會於6月17日舉行「撐到底！打工仔反送中大會」，表達打工仔的不滿。我們堅信，僱員有權以罷工方法表達對社會公義和人權的追求，理應得到尊重和保障。不少僱員原先已通知罷工，<span style=\"color: red;\">呼籲大家可繼續以罷工或其他可行方式參與是次集會</span>，提出以下訴求：<br />\n<br />\n1.林鄭下台；<br />\n2.立即撤回送中條例；<br />\n3.收回6.12「暴動」定性；<br />\n4.承諾對被捕人士不作檢控；<br />\n5.停止一切白色恐佈；<br />\n<br />\n詳情如下：<br />\n「撐到底！打工仔反送中大會」<br />\n日期：2019年6月17日(星期一)<br />\n時間：下午2:30-4:30<br />\n地點：金鐘龍匯道（中信大廈對出空地）<br />\n<br />\n香港職工會聯盟<br />\n2019年6月15日"},{"pid":"7ee31188c348422494faa194d7b96c93b0649e5c","tid":1228664,"uid":63311,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:40:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>最終目標：完全撤回送中惡法。釋放義士。<br />\n<br />\n暫你老母緩呀！！！<br />\n<br />\n呢場仗我地仲未打贏就已經有巴打以死相諫，唔好掉以輕心。<br />\n<br />\n星期日出去遊行。  星期一出去集會。<br />\n<br />\n你仲可以唔出黎？<br />\n</strong></span></span></blockquote>"},{"pid":"bd4ffb0cc8c51ce325da88bc4e5e9acf13c4dda8","tid":1228664,"uid":94327,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:41:10.000Z","msg":"push!!!"},{"pid":"2d6678603a536881e995f7b3423efb811addd16a","tid":1228664,"uid":94327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:42:05.000Z","msg":"push!!!"},{"pid":"8b1a4bffa5cd7db26142cb99dbfd4bf79a9593f7","tid":1228664,"uid":94327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:42:49.000Z","msg":"push!!!"},{"pid":"47ac39f7a65a9770c8ab54cff012493fdd8878d3","tid":1228664,"uid":27797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:43:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8320af0459534ce2876b21db1f34c806df2081cf","tid":1228664,"uid":193565,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:43:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0ca892c7197be39242677f9968cdf65ad76a1732","tid":1228664,"uid":94327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:44:12.000Z","msg":"push!!!"},{"pid":"23c0165d0f2958a38b88c2f6b4041636b0dbfa0a","tid":1228664,"uid":124894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:44:16.000Z","msg":"lm"},{"pid":"2bc1fa8386a7080786e6d0ca380ad3c88a234473","tid":1228664,"uid":64884,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:45:33.000Z","msg":"民陣真係爛泥扶唔上炳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"da9addb997a50b9829edcec8ca5ad78f12107c51","tid":1228664,"uid":162783,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:46:22.000Z","msg":"職都辭撚埋<br />\n打完仗再搵"},{"pid":"a7838f6ce5e36005026a5ebe210b7b6952947407","tid":1228664,"uid":94327,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:48:08.000Z","msg":"push!!!"},{"pid":"46412fd07aa60649d4eb0dbf0367f6b76e7c72ee","tid":1228664,"uid":7948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:49:23.000Z","msg":"幫推"},{"pid":"72fed5b62e14098a5d8dc0285298ab8319f70500","tid":1228664,"uid":76078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:49:52.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"72449